object.script:
dL=screen.drawLine dtf=screen.drawTriangleF ipn=input.getNumber cs=math.cos sn=math.sin rd=math.rad sC=screen.setColor function onTick() roll=ipn(1) Top=ipn(2) Pitch=ipn(3)*(-360) tilt=roll*360 rev=false if Top<0 then tilt=-tilt rev=true end ofS=Pitch l=300 roll=roll*6.28 end function clamp(n,min,max) if n>max then return max elseif n<min then return min else return n end end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() mx,my=w/2,h/2 sC(4,101,255) screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h)
uV,rV={sn(rd(tilt)+rd(180)),cs(rd(tilt)+rd(180))},{sn(rd(tilt)+rd(90)),cs(rd(tilt)+rd(90))} if rev then uV,rV={-uV[1],-uV[2]},{-rV[1],-rV[2]} end dtf(mx+(l+ofS)*uV[1]-(l*rV[1]),my+(l+ofS)*uV[2]-(l*rV[2]),mx+l*rV[1]+(ofS)*uV[1],my+l*rV[2]+(ofS)*uV[2],mx+(l*rV[1])+((l+ofS)*uV[1]),my+(l*rV[2])+((l+ofS)*uV[2])) sC(6,6,6) dtf(mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1]),my+((ofS-1)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2]),mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1])+(l*rV[1]),my+((ofS-1)*uV[2])+(l*rV[2]),mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1])+(l*rV[1])-((l-1)*uV[1]),my+((ofS-1)*uV[2])+(l*rV[2])-((l-1)*uV[2])) sC(170,170,170) dL(mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1]),my+((ofS-1)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2]),(mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1]),(my+((ofS-1)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])) dL(mx+((ofS-0.5)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1]),my+((ofS-0.5)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2]),(mx+((ofS-0.5)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1]),(my+((ofS-0.5)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])) dL(mx+((ofS-1.5)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1]),my+((ofS-1.5)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2]),(mx+((ofS-1.5)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1]),(my+((ofS-1.5)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])) for i=5,90,5 do sC(6,6,6) dL(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1])-(5*rV[1]),my+((ofS+i)*uV[2])-(5*rV[2]),(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1]))+(5*rV[1]),(my+((ofS+i)*uV[2]))+(5*rV[2])) end for i=-5,-90,-5 do sC(120,120,120) dL(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1])+(5*rV[1]),my+((ofS+i)*uV[2])+(5*rV[2]),(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1]))-(5*rV[1]),(my+((ofS+i)*uV[2]))-(5*rV[2])) end sC(0,0,0,100) screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h) sC(180,180,180) dL(4,h/2,w/2-4,h/2) dL(w/2+4,h/2,w-4,h/2) dL(w/2,h/2+4,w/2+4,h/2) dL(w/2,h/2+4,w/2-5,h/2-1) --dL(w/2-16,h/2,w/2-8,h/2) dL(w/2+16,h/2,w/2+8,h/2) dL(w/2-8,h/2,w/2-4,h/2+4) dL(w/2-4,h/2+4,w/2+1,h/2-1) dL(w/2+8,h/2,w/2+4,h/2+4) --dA(w/2+1*sn(roll*6.28-3.14),h/2+1*cs(roll*6.28-3.14),12,130-tilt,230-tilt)
end function dA(...) local x,y,r,a1,a2=... a1=a1 or 0 a2=a2 or 360 step=22.5 if a2<a1 then a2,a1=a1,a2 end local a,px,py,ox,oy,ar = false,0,0,0,0,0 repeat a=a and math.min(a+step,a2) or a1 ar=(a-90)*math.pi/180 px,py=x+r*cs(ar),y+r*sn(ar) if a~=a1 then dL(ox,oy,px,py) end ox,oy = px,py until(a>=a2) end

object.script:
dtb=screen.drawTextBox drt=screen.drawRect drf=screen.drawRectF osn=output.setNumber otb=output.setBool ipn=input.getNumber isCenter = false isFollow = true oX=0 oY=0 tgl2=false w,h=64,32 function onTick() cX=ipn(5) cY=ipn(6) z=ipn(7) iX=ipn(3) iY=ipn(4) touch=input.getBool(1) compass=math.rad(ipn(8)*-(360)) compass2=compass+math.rad(-90) otb(1,zoomin) otb(2,zoomout) otb(3,reset)
zoomin=touch and ipir(iX,iY,0,h/4,10,6) zoomout=touch and ipir(iX,iY,0,2*h/4,10,6) reset=touch and ipir(iX,iY,0,3*h/4,10,6) inputX = iX inputY = iY
if reset then focusZone=false end if touch and iX>8 then focusZone=true end if focusZone then if touch and iX>8 then tx,ty=map.screenToMap(dX,dY,z,w,h,iX,iY) end rcx,rcy=map.screenToMap(dX,dY,z,w,h,w/2,h/2) dX=rcx+((tx-rcx)*0.05) dY=rcy+((ty-rcy)*0.05) else dX=cX dY=cY end if reset then oX=0 oY=0 dX=cX dY=cY end if tgl then dX=wpxn dY=wpyn end xz,yz=100/z*math.cos(compass2),100/z*math.sin(compass2) if not touch then tgl2=false atp2=false end if toggle and not tgl2 then tgl2=true tgl = not tgl end osn(31,dX) osn(32,dY) xz1, yz1 = map.mapToScreen(dX, dY, z, w, h, cX, cY) end function ipir(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() screen.drawMap(dX,dY,z) screen.setColor(0,30,255) screen.drawLine(xz1,yz1,xz1+xz,yz1+yz) drt(w/2, h/2, 1, 1) drt(xz1, yz1, 1, 1) drawPointer(xz1,yz1+1,10,compass) screen.setColor(30,30,30,120) drf(0,0,10,h) screen.setColor(0,30,255) dtb(0,0,10,6,"ZM",0,0) dtb(0,h/4,10,6,"+",0,0) dtb(0,2*h/4,10,6,"-",0,0) dtb(0,3*h/4,10,6,"R",0,0)
screen.setColor(40,40,40,120)
if zoomin then drf(0,h/4,10,6) end if zoomout then drf(0,2*h/4,10,6) end if reset then drf(0,3*h/4,10,6) end
end function drawPointer(x,y,s,r,...) a=... a=(a or 30)*math.pi/360 x=x+s/2*math.sin(r) y=y-s/2*math.cos(r) screen.drawTriangleF(x,y,x-s*math.sin(r+a),y+s*math.cos(r+a),x-s*math.sin(r-a),y+s*math.cos(r-a)) end function setC(r,g,b) return r^2.2/255^2.2*r,g^2.2/255^2.2*g,b^2.2/255^2.2*b end
